            "Contract-misrepresentation focus: once expertise, reliance, or inducement is established, do not restate the same superior-knowledge/reliance narrative at length in each later section; refer back briefly and move to the next legal step.",
            "Contract-misrepresentation focus: apply rescission bars to the actual facts, including affirmation, lapse of time, third-party rights, and whether restitutio in integrum remains practically possible.",
